{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/auto-open-terminals-vs-code-workspace/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jack Harner","description":"Jack Harner is a Freelance Web Developer & E-Commerce Consultant based in Denver, Colorado. Shopify, BigCommerce, WordPress Dev & More.","author":"@jackharner","siteUrl":"https://jackharner.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Here's how to get VS Code to automatically open a couple terminals in your different workspace folders when you first open VS Code.</p>\n<p>Open your workspace settings with <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl + Shift + P</code> and then type Workspace Settings and select <code class=\"language-text\">Preferences: Open Workspace Settings (JSON)</code></p>\n<p>It should look something like this:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">\"folders\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"path\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"folder-1\"</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"path\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"folder-2\"</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">\"settings\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Add the following <code class=\"language-text\">tasks</code> object:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">\"folders\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">\"settings\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ADD THIS ⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️</span>\n\t<span class=\"token property\">\"tasks\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2.0.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"tasks\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t\t  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Frontend\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Change this</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"shell\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"icon\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token property\">\"id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"home\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"color\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"terminal.ansiBlue\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"isBackground\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"options\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t  <span class=\"token property\">\"cwd\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"${workspaceFolder:folder-1}\"</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// Change just the folder name</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"runOptions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"runOn\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"folderOpen\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"command\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/bin/bash\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;-- your shell here</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"presentation\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t  <span class=\"token property\">\"echo\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// silence \"Executing task ...\"</span>\n\t\t\t  <span class=\"token property\">\"focus\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t  <span class=\"token property\">\"panel\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"dedicated\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Backend\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"shell\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"icon\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token property\">\"id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"flame\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token property\">\"color\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"terminal.ansiRed\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"isBackground\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"options\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t  <span class=\"token property\">\"cwd\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"${workspaceFolder:folder-2}\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"runOptions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"runOn\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"folderOpen\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"command\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/bin/bash\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;-- your shell here</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"presentation\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t  <span class=\"token property\">\"echo\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// silence \"Executing task ...\"</span>\n\t\t\t  <span class=\"token property\">\"focus\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t  <span class=\"token property\">\"panel\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"dedicated\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>        \n\t\t  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Open\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"dependsOn\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Frontend\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Backend\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Make sure these match your above task labels</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token property\">\"runOptions\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"runOn\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"folderOpen\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\t  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Add This ⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Save the settings, then reload your window with <code class=\"language-text\">Ctrl + Shift + P</code>, typing <code class=\"language-text\">reload</code>, and selecting <code class=\"language-text\">Developer: Reload Window</code>. Your window should re-open along with whatever terminals you outlined above.</p>\n<p>Happy Coding!</p>\n<hr>\n<p><em>Photo by <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/@clemhlrdt?utm_content=creditCopyText&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=unsplash\">Clément Hélardot</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/black-and-silver-laptop-computer-on-table-95YRwf6CNw8?utm_content=creditCopyText&utm_medium=referral&utm_source=unsplash\">Unsplash</a></em></p>","excerpt":"Here's how to get VS Code to automatically open a couple terminals in your different workspace folders when you first open VS Code. Open your…","wordCount":{"words":75},"frontmatter":{"date":"June 18, 2024","updated":null,"title":"How To Auto-Open Multiple Terminals In A VS Code Workspace","subtitle":"Get To Coding Quicker","tags":["Automation","Life Hacks"],"featuredImage":{"absolutePath":"/home/runner/work/jackharner-gatsby/jackharner-gatsby/content/blog/auto-open-terminals-vs-code-workspace/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fullWidth","backgroundColor":"#b8b8b8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/5267c/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.jpg","srcSet":"/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/7284f/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.jpg 750w,\n/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/29ba9/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.jpg 1080w,\n/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/c8896/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.jpg 1366w,\n/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/5267c/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.jpg 1920w","sizes":"100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/57584/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.webp 750w,\n/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/984df/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.webp 1080w,\n/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/4a276/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.webp 1366w,\n/static/18ca1a35e60ca2b2ffabdc2fef0f713f/9c00f/clement-helardot-95YRwf6CNw8-unsplash.webp 1920w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"100vw"}]},"width":1,"height":0.6666666666666666}}},"ogImage":null},"fields":{"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »","slug":"/blog/auto-open-terminals-vs-code-workspace/","ogImage":"","date":"June 18, 2024","unlisted":false}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/auto-open-terminals-vs-code-workspace/","related":[{"id":"ee8fa99a-1147-5344-b53e-414466a0c0cc","excerpt":"WordPress Development relies on either Themes or Plugins for WordPress. Today, I'm going to walk you through the base files you need for any…","fields":{"date":"2023-01-13T00:21:19.284Z","slug":"/blog/anatomy-of-a-wordpress-theme/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Anatomy of a WordPress Theme","subtitle":"Required Template Files for Themes & Plugins","tags":["WordPress"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#989898","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/38042f6e79a703904fe1f0510053da47